article.description: — Marco Foster, Jayden Martinez and Nick Johnson each scored 13 points to lead New Hampshire to a 64-48 win over UMass Lowell on Tuesday night.
article.headline: Foster carries New Hampshire over UMass Lowell 64-48
article.linkText: Foster carries New Hampshire over UMass Lowell 64-48
article.story: LOWELL, Mass. -- — Marco Foster, Jayden Martinez and Nick Johnson each scored 13 points to lead New Hampshire to a 64-48 win over UMass Lowell on Tuesday night. Nick Guadarrama had 10 points and eight rebounds for New Hampshire (15-12, 10-8 America East Conference). Ayinde Hikim scored a career-high 22 points for the River Hawks (14-15, 6-11). The Wildcats improve to 2-0 against the River Hawks on the season. New Hampshire defeated UMass Lowell 67-61 on Jan. 22. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
